# Monorepo-wide ignores
node_modules/
**/.svelte-kit/
**/build/
**/.output/
**/.vercel/
**/.netlify/
**/.wrangler/
**/dist/
**/test-results/
**/.turbo/
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.test

# Per-machine overrides for tool-agnostic workflow contracts (workflow v0.6.0 R4-1).
# Real Notion UUIDs and other workspace-specific config live in *.local.md files
# so the committed AGENTS.md / CLAUDE.md stay fork-safe.
*.local.md
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
bun.lockb
vite.config.js.timestamp-*
vite.config.ts.timestamp-*
.remember/
.worktrees/
.superpowers/brainstorm/
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
Weather_API_Key.txt

# SVGO source backups kept local only — committed file is the optimized source of truth
apps/web/static/images/*.source.svg

# Migrated to Notion (Phase 2 — Notion is the single source of truth)
/docs/project/
/docs/roadmap/
/docs/ops/
/docs/README.md
/docs/superpowers/specs/
/docs/superpowers/research/
/docs/superpowers/plans/
/docs/slices/
/docs/sessions/
/docs/ARCHIVE.md
/docs/_TEMPLATES/
/brand/BRAND.md
/brand/components.md
/brand/README.md
/brand/foundations/*.md
/brand/decisions/*.md
/brand/examples/README.md

# NOT ignored (stays tracked):
#   /docs/ai-memory/, /docs/reference/{tools, WORKFLOW.md}
# (brand/ and docs/superpowers/plans/ fully removed in chore/post-merge-cleanup PR.)
